Class HarvCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.ps18.model.board.boardcells.HarvCell

  • public class HarvCell
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a harvest cell.
    When a family member is placed, this cell activates a set of permanent effects if conditions are fulfilled.

    yazan-matar
